org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi

Interface BooleanMonitor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItemFeatureEntry
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BooleanMonitorImpl

    public interface BooleanMonitor
extends ItemFeatureEntry
    A representation of the model object 'Boolean Monitor'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Reference Value
    • Active
    • Demote Prefix
    • Severity
    • Message
    • Suppress Events
    • Require Ack

    See Also:
    OsgiPackage.getBooleanMonitor()
